{"tid":29942,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"經常流鼻血","createTime":"2016-12-09T02:03:32.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T06:41:01.000Z","uid":15897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"649557e52f55e2e7d00bc88aa66d1553713835cc","tid":29942,"uid":15897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T02:03:32.000Z","msg":"小弟最近成日流鼻血<br />\n經常瞓醒見到枕頭有血跡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 飲涼茶有冇用？"},{"pid":"64b4904fb8ff74e160cfa5aa5b6aca93fd852087","tid":29942,"uid":23493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T02:04:29.000Z","msg":"可能天氣乾燥，但睇下醫生好喎"},{"pid":"9ff20e3efd1ccc3925ac2a0d044c9a1c65a6f732","tid":29942,"uid":39207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T02:05:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"11b0888e39777a0e70bafc10e66c4247d073fef3","tid":29942,"uid":39207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T02:05:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5ae552554f734b82cfef97f1c2003f949e8882f8","tid":29942,"uid":22287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T02:06:46.000Z","msg":"一係天氣乾 , 一係鼻咽癌"},{"pid":"58d86ce96b0121d0f953e5a697ff1226093674a9","tid":29942,"uid":50815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T02:13:34.000Z","msg":"睇醫生啦仲問<br />\n成日流鼻血好多原因"},{"pid":"ae075eec885857e17627a47acfce2ee88b75b7c3","tid":29942,"uid":33957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T03:02:10.000Z","msg":"我都成日瘋狂流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次流之前 個人就會feel到熱一熱<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後次次流5分鐘"},{"pid":"519c30a0f5cb77b658c2dfe998cc7a3ffeb36647","tid":29942,"uid":49802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T16:14:06.000Z","msg":"會唔會覺得個鼻好乾？<br />\n可以試吓臨瞓前揸少少 vaseline入鼻lone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cfca16f67a3992b74f0ef650f1a8217148533a3","tid":29942,"uid":2949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T16:18:57.000Z","msg":"流鼻血淨係流一邊其實係咪正常？我永遠得右邊會流，左邊無流過咁滯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57f16086cda5e88ebbf3fd211b1ac8b0ad3e53ad","tid":29942,"uid":17091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T16:21:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>流鼻血淨係流一邊其實係咪正常？我永遠得右邊會流，左邊無流過咁滯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我上個月 日日流一次 而且出血量都幾多<br />\n都係全部右邊<br />\nkeep 住流左3個星期 最嚴重果日一日流左3次<br />\n跟住一入冬即刻無流過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de3066035a175ff789b36bfb0606152419b47ced","tid":29942,"uid":2949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T17:05:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>流鼻血淨係流一邊其實係咪正常？我永遠得右邊會流，左邊無流過咁滯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我上個月 日日流一次 而且出血量都幾多<br />\n都係全部右邊<br />\nkeep 住流左3個星期 最嚴重果日一日流左3次<br />\n跟住一入冬即刻無流過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我通常係果日feel到個鼻窿唔太暢通 搵手撩兩撩 之後隻手指濕濕地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一流起碼十分鐘"},{"pid":"ec5dca85fc447cc19549a9c4c205fa6f90971530","tid":29942,"uid":27492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:41:01.000Z","msg":"由細到大都成日流<br />\n呢排又日日都黎料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}